    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against required level 3 due to single-condition ASTM F1717 testing; gap accepted because F1717 loading is conservative relative to in vivo estimates and consistent with regulatory precedent for this device class. All three QoIs satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and relative error < 10%. Model credibility is sufficient to support the Medium-risk COU decision.",
